    <div class="post-body" itemprop="articleBody"><h2 id="无穷级数"><a href="#无穷级数" class="headerlink" title="无穷级数"></a>无穷级数</h2><p>等比数列</p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601790764370.png" alt="1601790764370"></p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601790914893.png" alt="1601790914893"></p>
<p>例题</p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601791340789.png" alt="1601791340789"></p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601791680034.png" alt="1601791680034"></p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601792414977.png" alt="1601792414977"></p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601793241870.png" alt="1601793241870"></p>
<h5 id="调和级数"><a href="#调和级数" class="headerlink" title="调和级数"></a>调和级数</h5><blockquote>
<p>调和级数是发散的</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601793542661.png" alt="1601793542661"></p>
<h4 id="性质"><a href="#性质" class="headerlink" title="性质"></a>性质</h4><p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601793732086.png" alt="1601793732086"></p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601793936645.png" alt="1601793936645"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>相反则未必</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601794096106.png" alt="1601794096106"></p>
<p>敛散性不变</p>
<p>如果级数收敛，通项是趋于0的。</p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601794310032.png" alt="1601794310032"></p>
<ul>
<li><p>通项趋于0，未必是收敛的，</p>
</li>
<li><p>通项不趋于0，一定是不收敛的。</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601794730888.png" alt="1601794730888"></p>
<p>例题：</p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601795245209.png" alt="1601795245209"></p>
<p>通项不趋于0必发散</p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601795312952.png" alt="1601795312952"></p>
<p>去掉了第一项，敛散性不变</p>
<h2 id="正项级数"><a href="#正项级数" class="headerlink" title="正项级数"></a>正项级数</h2><p>大收必小收 小散必大散</p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601804217057.png" alt="1601804217057"></p>
<p>例题</p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601804688577.png" alt="1601804688577"></p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601805099865.png" alt="1601805099865"></p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601805233170.png" alt="1601805233170"></p>
<p>公式</p>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601825215690.png" alt="1601825215690"></p>
<h4 id="例题"><a href="#例题" class="headerlink" title="例题"></a>例题</h4><p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601825904805.png" alt="1601825904805"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>等于1说明分子分母有相同的敛散性,1&#x2F;n是发散的</p>
</blockquote>
<p><img data-src="https://cdn.kayleh.top/gh/kayleh/cdn/img/%E7%BA%A7%E6%95%B0/1601826789198.png" alt="1601826789198"></p>
